## Code Example

```tsx
<LeftNavigation selectedItem="INVOICES">
  <LeftNavigation.Group>
    <LeftNavigation.Item label="Transactions" itemId="TRANSACTIONS">
      <LeftNavigation.Item label="Invoices" itemId="INVOICES" />
      <LeftNavigation.Item label="Expenses" itemId="EXPENSES" />
    </LeftNavigation.Item>
  </LeftNavigation.Group>
</LeftNavigation>
```

